@import ./_tui.convo

> user
Add more complete keyboard handling for input sprites.

Goals:
- Support Delete.
- Support Home and End.
- Support left/right cursor movement inside input text.
- Support paste handling without treating escape/control sequences as printable text.
- Use the input caret state introduced for cursor positioning.
- Keep single-line input behavior for now unless multiline is already naturally supported.

Acceptance criteria:
- Backspace removes the character before the caret.
- Delete removes the character at the caret.
- Left/right arrows move the caret within the input value when an input sprite is active.
- Home moves the caret to the start.
- End moves the caret to the end.
- Printable pasted text is inserted at the caret.
- `onInput` fires when the input value changes.
- Existing focus navigation and click activation still work.

Update notes at the end of your response
